# Model-Agnostic Intelligence

Read **[MODEL_AGNOSTIC_INTELLIGENCE.md](../../MODEL_AGNOSTIC_INTELLIGENCE.md)** before adding AI generation, provider SDKs, or model configuration.

## Rules

1. **Aipify Intelligence is the product** — customers purchase Aipify, not GPT/Claude/Gemini
2. Route all generation through `lib/intelligence/` (`selectModelProfile`) — never hardcode a provider at skill/UI layer
3. **Never** expose model provider brands in customer-facing UI or copy
4. Select model **by task** (executive summary, support, recommendations, retrieval, email draft)
5. Enterprise may use `customer_approved` policy with approved profile IDs — default is `aipify_managed`
6. Learning, trust, approvals, and tenancy must remain independent of any single provider SDK
7. Provider adapters belong in Core services — swappable without changing Customer App or skills

> Models may change. Aipify remains.
